**What the document covers:**

| Section | Content |
|---|---|
| **1. Data Models** | Full schema breakdown for User Profile, Study Plan, Vocabulary, Mistakes, Progress/Sessions, Activity/Consistency, and Saved Content — with field types, storage source, and access API for each |
