| **5. Gaps & Recommendations** | 6 missing triggers (`missed_task`, `lesson_completed`, `falling_behind_plan`, etc.) and a recommended integration flow diagram from storage → learning engine → AI Tutor |

**Key finding:** `NextBestAction[]` from the Learning Engine is the richest pre-computed suggestion source but is currently not consumed by the AI Tutor — bridging this gap would enable most of the desired proactive scenarios.
